## About the Project

**Proxidize MX2 Manager** was created by Fawaz Al-Ghzawi to address the real-world challenges of managing large Proxidize MX2 cellular modem deployments. This tool bridges the gap between individual modem management and enterprise-scale operations, providing a professional-grade solution that handles the complexity of multi-threaded operations while maintaining an intuitive user interface.

